This is a Barnes-Hut simulator written on top of Charm++

To build:
	- Edit the Makefile CHARM_PATH to point to your built copy of Charm++ 

	- Edit the Makefile STRUCTURES_PATH to point to the Changa structures library
		git clone https://github.com/N-BodyShop/utility
		STRUCTURES_PATH = utility/structures

	- make

Usage:

# Prepare a data file with 10K particles:
./plummer 10000 particles.bin

# Run on a single processor
./charmrun +p1 ./barnes -in=particles.bin -p=100  -killat=50




